CAS

The Central Authorization System is intended as a fairly simple yet robust
sytem for managing user logins and permissions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc CAS

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CAS

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=CAS

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/CAS

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/CAS

